# Quick Calculations

Showcasing CalcMark's domain-specific features in one-liners.
An agent can pipe any of these: `echo "expression" | cm --format json`

## Unit Conversions

marathon = 42.195 km in miles
5 gallons in liters

## Rate Conversion and Accumulation

1200 req/s per minute
api_rate = 1200 req/s
convert_rate(api_rate, hour)

500 MB/day over 1 year

## Capacity Planning

50000 req/s at 2000 req/s per server with 25% buffer

## Napkin Math

~10M users * ~2 KB as napkin

## Date Arithmetic

deadline = Jun 30 2026
remaining = deadline - today
kickoff = 6 weeks from today

## Financial Growth

compound $10000 by 7% over 30 years
compound $10000 by 7% monthly over 30 years
depreciate $50000 by 15% over 5 years to $5000

## Percentage Widening

$250 + 8.25%
$250 - 20%
15% of $2000

## Storage I/O

read 100 MB from ssd
compress 1 GB using gzip

## Network

rtt(regional)
transfer 500 KB across regional gigabit
downtime(99.9%, month)
